snippet.title: NumWorlds - My Indie Game for 15 seconds
snippet.description:
Welcome to NumWorlds, the perfect game for those moments when you need a mindful break or just want to flex those cognitive muscles. Discover the gorgeous underwater world of Atlantis and its 100 levels packed with interesting challenges and delightful mini-games to give a rest to your brain cells.

Download it today on iOS and Android!
